":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黃金拼圖第一季第一集咁多(英國Alice老家＋LONDON)<br />\n點兔唔使講, 法國小鎮.<br />\n因為水星去左2次Venice<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n異國迷路就中古巴黎</blockquote><br />\nmarked. thx for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我睇完水星，打算2018面具節就去真威尼斯搵社長同大貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃金拼圖令我諗起佢d英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃圖找左COCO塾外語監修, Alice CV揀過要英文發音. 雖然私心東山好聽D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36d37be86b100a742edad787e35e836fbc34fb9","tid":369591,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黃金拼圖第一季第一集咁多(英國Alice老家＋LONDON)<br />\n點兔唔使講, 法國小鎮.<br />\n因為水星去左2次Venice<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n異國迷路就中古巴黎</blockquote><br />\nmarked. thx for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我睇完水星，打算2018面具節就去真威尼斯搵社長同大貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係今年Carnevale 去左第二次. 雖然係未來火星聖巡, 但有今生無來世丫. 仲有劇場版最後REUNION個蝸牛府(Palazzo Contarini del Bovolo)天台今年裝修完開返. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-v58u-V4PHL8/WMjF7fGKJ8I/AAAAAAAAdww/coGo4xqupPY61ne43I1LUjcoGpzD-mQxQCEw/s1600/20170213-120512-25442528.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-v58u-V4PHL8%2FWMjF7fGKJ8I%2FAAAAAAAAdww%2FcoGo4xqupPY61ne43I1LUjcoGpzD-mQxQCEw%2Fs1600%2F20170213-120512-25442528.JPG&h=50e8ca7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-UPHHhcen8e4/WLTuuOeDViI/AAAAAAAAdLY/rC61BrKyXv4V4KwdpTxv8XJy8BuAr7fmwCEw/s1600/20170213-183848-25552528.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail